I don't think so. I think eq only touches the UI file (UI_charname_##) if you're loading the new UI. So any changes you made for the new UI should still be intact when you run the new UI again.<br>
<br>
A Guide told me, sometimes if your body doesn't disappear when you 'fully loot' your corpse. You can try reverting back to the old UI and you may see the items that were presumably missing.<br>
<br>
I got my items back. The GM admin basically said, they currently don't know what is causing the items to disappear. I asked him what should I do to avoid this from happening again. He said, &quot;Don't die!  &quot;. For me death and fun go hand in hand so I've just reverted back to the old UI until they get the issue sorted out. It's a pity because I really like they way they've implemented the pet health and command system.<br>
